snippet.title: DragonSlayer : Legend of Heroes (TURBOGRAFX CD) Part 1
snippet.description:
I have an old video game magazine mentioning this game,on how the beginning of the game is so remarkable,and the rest of the game was a big wetdown. I kinda agree,since now you control what seems to be a  grade 1 prince(with a 50 year old voice actor)
and batlle screens that doesn't rival nintendo(NES)  at all.

Still, a refreshing change to say the least.
